Lux Island Resorts Ltd. (NRL) , a
Mauritian leisure operator, plans to expand its operations
through management of hotels in Indian Ocean island nations, the
Persian Gulf, Africa or Haiti, Port Louis-based Le Defi
Quotidien reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Paul Jones.  To contact the reporter on this story:
